title: Superman Post-Crisis Chronology v5 Part 8
description:
Covering chapters 176-200

Highlights:
-Ra&#039;s Al Ghul strikes the JLA in the Tower of Babel!
-Joker gains Mxyzptlk&#039;s powers and becomes Emperor Joker!
-Supergirl and the other Earthborn angels battle the Carnivore!
-Lex Luthor is elected President of the USA!
-Superman battles Manchester Black&#039;s Elite!
-Superman first visits Brainiac&#039;s faux Krypton in Return to Krypton I!
-The Guardian dies and is reborn!
-Imperiex arrives at Earth in Our Worlds at War!
-Joker (man, that guy had a busy year) finds out he&#039;s dying and decides to go out with a Last Laugh!
